## GraphQL 스키마

```graphql
# schema.graphql
type Query {
  me: User
  user(id: ID!): User
  users(limit: Int = 20, offset: Int = 0): [User!]!
  post(id: ID!): Post
  feed(limit: Int = 20, cursor: String): FeedConnection!
}

type Mutation {
  register(input: RegisterInput!): AuthPayload!
  login(email: String!, password: String!): AuthPayload!
  createPost(content: String!, images: [String!]): Post!
  likePost(postId: ID!): Post!
  addComment(postId: ID!, content: String!): Comment!
  followUser(userId: ID!): User!
}

type User {
  id: ID!
  username: String!
  displayName: String!
  bio: String
  avatarUrl: String
  posts: [Post!]!
  followerCount: Int!
  followingCount: Int!
  isFollowing: Boolean!
}

type Post {
  id: ID!
  content: String!
  images: [String!]!
  author: User!
  likeCount: Int!
  isLiked: Boolean!
  comments: [Comment!]!
  createdAt: String!
}

type Comment {
  id: ID!
  content: String!
  author: User!
  createdAt: String!
}

type AuthPayload {
  token: String!
  user: User!
}

type FeedConnection {
  edges: [Post!]!
  pageInfo: PageInfo!
}

type PageInfo {
  hasNextPage: Boolean!
  endCursor: String
}

input RegisterInput {
  username: String!
  email: String!
  password: String!
  displayName: String!
}
```

## 리졸버

```typescript
// resolvers/user.ts
export const userResolvers = {
  Query: {
    me: async (_, __, { userId, prisma }) => {
      if (!userId) throw new Error("로그인 필요");
      return prisma.user.findUnique({ where: { id: userId } });
    },

    users: async (_, { limit, offset }, { prisma }) => {
      return prisma.user.findMany({ take: limit, skip: offset });
    },
  },

  User: {
    posts: (user, _, { prisma }) =>
      prisma.post.findMany({ where: { authorId: user.id } }),

    followerCount: (user, _, { prisma }) =>
      prisma.follow.count({ where: { followingId: user.id } }),

    followingCount: (user, _, { prisma }) =>
      prisma.follow.count({ where: { followerId: user.id } }),

    isFollowing: async (user, _, { userId, prisma }) => {
      if (!userId) return false;
      const follow = await prisma.follow.findUnique({
        where: { followerId_followingId: { followerId: userId, followingId: user.id } },
      });
      return !!follow;
    },
  },

  Mutation: {
    createPost: async (_, { content, images }, { userId, prisma }) => {
      if (!userId) throw new Error("로그인 필요");
      return prisma.post.create({
        data: { content, images: images || [], authorId: userId },
      });
    },

    likePost: async (_, { postId }, { userId, prisma }) => {
      const existing = await prisma.like.findUnique({
        where: { userId_postId: { userId, postId } },
      });

      if (existing) {
        await prisma.like.delete({ where: { id: existing.id } });
      } else {
        await prisma.like.create({ data: { userId, postId } });
      }

      return prisma.post.findUnique({ where: { id: postId } });
    },
  },
};
```

## 서버 실행

```typescript
// server.ts
import { ApolloServer } from "@apollo/server";
import { expressMiddleware } from "@apollo/server/express4";
import express from "express";
import { PrismaClient } from "@prisma/client";
import { readFileSync } from "fs";
import { userResolvers } from "./resolvers/user";
import { verifyToken } from "./utils/auth";

const prisma = new PrismaClient();
const typeDefs = readFileSync("schema.graphql", "utf-8");

const server = new ApolloServer({ typeDefs, resolvers: userResolvers });

async function main() {
  await server.start();
  const app = express();

  app.use("/graphql", express.json(), expressMiddleware(server, {
    context: async ({ req }) => {
      const token = req.headers.authorization?.replace("Bearer ", "");
      const userId = token ? verifyToken(token) : null;
      return { userId, prisma };
    },
  }));

  app.listen(4000, () => console.log("GraphQL: http://localhost:4000/graphql"));
}

main();
```

REST 대비 GraphQL은 클라이언트가 필요한 데이터만 요청할 수 있어 효율적입니다.

